levels.name: Toe Taps
levels.details: Keeping the ball stationary, tap the top of the ball with the soles of both feet

levels.name: Bell Taps
levels.details: Transfer ball from side to side in a “bell ringing” motion, using the inside of both feet

levels.name: Inside Outside
levels.details: Move the ball between both feet using the inside and outside of the foot

levels.name: Rocking Sole
levels.details: Rock the ball from side to side using the sole of the foot

levels.name: Sole Rolls
levels.details: Transfer the ball from one foot to the other by rolling the foot over the ball

levels.name: Sole Inside Push
levels.details: Trap the ball underneath the foot and roll foot outwards to push ball across with the inside of foot

levels.name: Brazilian Trap
levels.details: Roll the ball across the body then trap the ball with the opposite sole of the foot behind standing leg

levels.name: Gustavs specialare
levels.details: Roll the ball across the body then trap the ball with the opposite sole of the foot behind standing leg
